{"id":43765,"date":"2024-01-22T10:04:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-22T04:34:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=43765"},"modified":"2023-03-23T20:30:00","modified_gmt":"2023-03-23T15:00:00","slug":"stylish-ladder-shelves","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/stylish-ladder-shelves\/","title":{"rendered":"Ladder Shelves: Stylish Storage At Minimal Costs"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This is how you style a ladder shelf to achieve that effortless boho vibe in your house.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Which is the easiest DIY project that will instantly organise your home and yet look like you ordered it from that fancy decor catalogue? Yes, the humble ladder shelf.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apart from ease, another factor makes the ladder shelf a dependable decor element for every accommodation. It looks as much at home in a luxe, mid-century apartment as in a bachelor pad with an industrial theme. Or we could place that decorative ladder shelf in the entryway, near the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/couch-designs-for-living-room\/\">living room couch<\/a>, next to the basin in the washroom, in the kitchen pantry or on the balcony- does it look out of place anywhere? Not at all. Chances are it looks like it was made for the place where it is positioned.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>How about materials? A metal ladder shelf is suitable for the more moisture-ridden spaces, while a wooden ladder shelf will grace the living rooms and bedrooms best. An acrylic or plastic ladder shelf will be ideal for vertical plant decor.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ladder shelves are synonymous with versatility. They come in different heights, with varying widths, and are priced for all budgets. The ladder shelf spectrum is bright and busy. We gathered our best ladder shelf designs to offer ideas on why you need them now. Take a look.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Ladder Shelf Adds Height<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most furniture is barely 30-36 inches off the ground. The sofas, bed, tables and chairs are at a similar height level in any room. The only element that can create vertical visual interest is the artwork on the walls. A ladder shelf invites the eye upwards and breaks the monotony of the same-height furniture. It adds a 3D point of interest and adds depth to any room. Add exciting accessories corresponding to the room, and the unassuming ladder shelf becomes the star of the show.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201545\/ladder-shelf-adds-height.jpg\" alt=\"Ladder shelf adds height\" class=\"wp-image-43771\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201545\/ladder-shelf-adds-height.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201545\/ladder-shelf-adds-height-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201545\/ladder-shelf-adds-height-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201545\/ladder-shelf-adds-height-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Ladder shelves are a prized possession in visual real estate<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Ladder Shelf Provides Stylish Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pairing functionality with great aesthetics is a right up ladder shelf\u2019s alley. Vertical storage takes up less space and reduces visual clutter. Be it the bedroom where you want to hang your hats, bags or even clothes, or a washroom where the towels, faux plants, bottles and toilet rolls need to be placed- a ladder shelf is useful in both scenarios.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201539\/ladder-shelf-provides-stylish-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Ladder shelf provides stylish storage\" class=\"wp-image-43770\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201539\/ladder-shelf-provides-stylish-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201539\/ladder-shelf-provides-stylish-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201539\/ladder-shelf-provides-stylish-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201539\/ladder-shelf-provides-stylish-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Glam up your closet with ladder shelves<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Ladder Shelf Is Affordable<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Furniture costs a bomb. A wooden bookshelf will empty your wallet, but a ladder shelf of similar material and height will be priced much lesser. If you choose to go for metal ladder shelves, they will amount to even lower. Add height to a room without going broke? Why not?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201531\/ladder-shelf-is-affordable.jpg\" alt=\"Ladder shelf is affordable\" class=\"wp-image-43769\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201531\/ladder-shelf-is-affordable.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201531\/ladder-shelf-is-affordable-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201531\/ladder-shelf-is-affordable-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201531\/ladder-shelf-is-affordable-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Metal ladder shelves are highly affordable and look sleek<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Ladder Shelf Do Away With Other Furniture<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A ladder shelf replaces <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedside-table-designs\/\">bedside tables<\/a>, nesting tables, cabinets, bookshelves and chest of drawers quite effortlessly. Depending on where you choose to place it, you can subtract the need for additional furniture. This makes for a more sustainable and eco-friendly living while ensuring that mobility is preserved. A ladder shelf is a perfect solution for those who live in apartments and change homes often. Choose a cool ladder shelf to display that enviable book obsession or that scented candle collection. Place it at the entrance with a mirror and you can always steal a last look at yourself before heading out. This same ladder shelf can as easily replace a vanity in the bedroom.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201524\/ladder-shelf-do-away-with-other-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Ladder shelf do away with other furniture\" class=\"wp-image-43768\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201524\/ladder-shelf-do-away-with-other-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201524\/ladder-shelf-do-away-with-other-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201524\/ladder-shelf-do-away-with-other-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201524\/ladder-shelf-do-away-with-other-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A ladder shelf in the bathroom is almost a must<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Multifunctional home interiors with eye catching aesthetics!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/06165540\/multifunctional-home-interiors-with-eye-catching-aesthetics-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Ladder Shelf Is Airy<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ladder shelves are open and airy. It\u2019s a breeze to clean them. There\u2019s another upside to the open layout. When fascinating curios and decor pieces are placed, they add more charm to the room. If the open display is not your thing, you could put stuff in colourful storage boxes or play around with different prints and textures. This way, you can keep your stuff hidden while still keeping the space compelling.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201518\/ladder-shelf-is-airy.jpg\" alt=\"Ladder shelf is airy\" class=\"wp-image-43767\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201518\/ladder-shelf-is-airy.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201518\/ladder-shelf-is-airy-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201518\/ladder-shelf-is-airy-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201518\/ladder-shelf-is-airy-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The kitchen area has come alive with a ladder shelf\u2019s smart storage <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If the standard ladder shelf is not your choice, you could use s-hooks and hang baskets as an alternative. They look different and chic. The minimal design of a ladder shelf appeals to every sensibility. The stores are replete with these busy bees in exciting designs, but with a little effort and perseverance, you can either create your own or have one constructed through the local carpenter.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201510\/ladder-shelf-in-the-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Ladder shelf in the bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-43766\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201510\/ladder-shelf-in-the-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201510\/ladder-shelf-in-the-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201510\/ladder-shelf-in-the-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23201510\/ladder-shelf-in-the-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Ladder shelf in the bedroom clears up floor space <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ladder shelves are the new <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">interior design<\/a> hack to store all those odds and ends that we can\u2019t seem to get rid of. These simple design tools complement all decor themes. They are easy to move, easier to construct and elevate every space. So, get creative with your display solutions and storage options with stylish ladder shelves.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"for